Fix CVE-2025-68384: Add user profile size limit to prevent DoS via oversized profiles

This patch adds a configurable size limit (xpack.security.profile.max_size) for user
profiles stored in Elasticsearch. The limit prevents large profiles from exhausting
heap memory and impacting cluster stability.

Upstream-Fix: https://github.com/elastic/elasticsearch/pull/137712
Upstream-Commit: ab1d99ae033f2a23a8856b47a2d86652ad63a39a
CVE: CVE-2025-68384
CWE: CWE-770

